{
  "openapi": "3.0.0",
  "info": {
    "description": "<h2>API for sending commands to <i>Aidwatch devices</i>.<br></h2> <a href=\"https://aidwatch.ch/\">Follow the Aidwatch site</a> <br> <br> <h2>General</h2> <p>Using this API, a client can send some information to an Aidwatch device (hereinafter referred to as <i>device</i>). <br>This API uses <a href=\"https://firebase.google.com/docs/cloud-messaging\">Firebase Cloud Messaging</a> to send data to <i>devices</i>. <br>The data is presented in the form of commands that <i>a device</i> can execute.</p> <br> <br> <h2>Structure</h2> <p>API consists of two endpoints:</p> <ol>\n  <li><i><a href=\"#/Device/post_api_sender_subscribeDevice\">Subscribe device</a></i> - The endpoint will be used to subscribe a <i>device</i> and send commands to it.</li>\n  <li><i><a href=\"#/Device/post_api_sender_sendCommand\">Send command</a></i> - The endpoint for sending a command to a subscribed <i>device</i>. </li>\n</ol> <br> <br> <h2>Process</h2> <p>The whole process of sending commands to a <i>device</i> is presented in the sequence diagram:<p> <br> <img src=\"https://aidwatch.s3.amazonaws.com/documentation/Aidwatch+Firebase+API+Sequence+Diagram+v0.0.3.jpg\"></img> <br> <br> <h3>Flow 1</h3> <ol> <li>Before a request to the <i>Aidwatch Firebase API</i>, a device has to get an authentication token from <i>KeyCloak</i> server. </li> </ol> <h3>Flow 2</h3> <ol> <li>Firstly a <i>device</i> has to subscribe to sending data from <i>Aidwatch Firebase API</i>. </li> <li>The API, in turn, sends a response about the success of the subscription request. </li> </ol> <h3>Flow 3</h3> <ol> <li>After these steps, a user can send commands to the <i>device</i>.</li> <li>After <i>Aidwatch Firebase API</i> has received a command from the user, he sends a request to <i>Firebase Cloud Messaging</i> to send a data (command) to the <i>device</i> and sends a response to the user. <p> Firebase sends data as a key pair. Examples: <table> <th>Example 1</th> <th>Example 2</th> <th>Example 3</th> <th>Example 4</th> <tr style=\"font-size: 12px; color: brown\"> <td>\n  CommandId = 1234<br>\n  CommandName = \"HEARTRATE\"<br>\n  CommandType = \"GET\"<br>\n  CommandActive = \"ON\"<br>\n</td> <td>\n  CommandId = 1234<br>\n  CommandName = \"FALLSENSOR\"<br>\n  CommandType = \"SET\"<br>\n  CommandActive = \"ON\"<br>\n  Threshold = \"1\" <br>\n  ScreenDelay = \"13\"\n</td> <td>\n  CommandId = 1234<br>\n  CommandName = \"WATCHREMOVE\"<br>\n  CommandType = \"SET\"<br>\n  CommandActive = \"OFF\"<br>\n  StartTime = \"12:30\"<br>\n  EndTime = \"18:00\"\n</td> <td>\n  CommandId = 1234<br>\n  CommandName = \"EMERGENCYNO\"<br>\n  CommandType = \"GET\"<br>\n  CommandActive = \"OFF\"<br>\n  Sequence1 = \"1\"<br>\n  Firstname1 = \"John\"<br>\n  Lastname1 = \"Doe\"<br>\n  Gender1 = \"M\"<br>\n  Email1 = \"john.doe@domain.com\"<br>\n  Telno1 = \"+41798252123\"<br>\n  Sequence2 = \"2\"<br>\n  Firstname2 = \"Jane\"<br>\n  Lastname2 = \"Doe\"<br>\n  Gender2 = \"F\"<br>\n  Email2 = \"jane.doe@domain.com\"<br>\n  Telno2 = \"+41798252321\"<br>\n</td> </tr> </table>\n</li> <li>The <i>device</i>, in turn, processes the received command and send a response to the <i>Device Response API</i></li>",
    "version": "2.0.2",
    "title": "Aidwatch Firebase API",
    "contact": {
      "email": "company@implemica.com"
    },
    "x-jentic-source-url": "https://api.swaggerhub.com/apis/implemica/aidwatch-firebase-api/2.0.2/swagger.json"
  },
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "Device",
      "description": "AidWatch device"
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/subscribeDevice": {
      "post": {
        "security": [
          {
            "OAuth2": [
              "subscribe_device"
            ]
          }
        ],
        "tags": [
          "Device"
        ],
        "summary": "Subscribes an Aidwatch device.",
        "description": "Subscribes an Aidwatch device for sending commands using Firebase Cloud Messaging API.\n<br>\nTo do this, a device has to send to the endpoint:\n  1. a token which is used to identify and authorize the device instance.\n  2. a device ID which use to identify an Aidwatch device.\n",
        "requestBody": {
          "$ref": "#/components/requestBodies/DeviceInfo"
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Device successfully subscribed.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SubscribedDevice"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "Authorization information is missing or invalid.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "403": {
            "description": "Access token does not have the required scope",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "Something wrong.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/sendCommand": {
      "post": {
        "security": [
          {
            "OAuth2": [
              "send_command"
            ]
          }
        ],
        "tags": [
          "Device"
        ],
        "summary": "Sends a command to an Aidwatch device.",
        "description": "Sends a command to a device.\n",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SendCommandDto"
              },
              "examples": {
                "FALLSENSOR": {
                  "value": {
                    "command": {
                      "name": "FALLSENSOR",
                      "commandType": "GET",
                      "commandActive": "ON",
                      "threshold": 1,
                      "screenDelay": 13
                    },
                    "deviceId": 1,
                    "timestamp": 1575812839756
                  }
                },
                "WATCHREMOVE": {
                  "value": {
                    "command": {
                      "name": "WATCHREMOVE",
                      "commandType": "GET",
                      "commandActive": "OFF",
                      "startTime": "08:30",
                      "endTime": "12:41"
                    },
                    "deviceId": 1,
                    "timestamp": 1575812839756
                  }
                },
                "LOWBATTERY": {
                  "value": {
                    "command": {
                      "name": "LOWBATTERY",
                      "commandType": "SET",
                      "commandActive": "OFF",
                      "minBattery": 12
                    },
                    "deviceId": 1,
                    "timestamp": 1575812839756
                  }
                },
                "WATCHSWITCHOFF": {
                  "value": {
                    "command": {
                      "name": "WATCHSWITCHOFF",
                      "commandType": "SET",
                      "commandActive": "ON"
                    },
                    "deviceId": 1,
                    "timestamp": 1575812839756
                  }
                },
                "MEDICINEALERT": {
                  "value": {
                    "command": {
                      "name": "MEDICINEALERT",
                      "commandType": "GET",
                      "commandActive": "ON",
                      "alarmTimes": [
                        "08:00",
                        "12:00",
                        "18:00"
                      ]
                    },
                    "deviceId": 1,
                    "timestamp": 1575812839756
                  }
                },
                "PEDOMETER": {
                  "value": {
                    "command": {
                      "name": "PEDOMETER",
                      "commandType": "GET",
                      "commandActive": "OFF",
                      "startTime": "08:30",
                      "endTime": "12:41"
                    },
                    "deviceId": 1,
                    "timestamp": 1575812839756
                  }
                },
                "SLEEPMONITOR": {
                  "value": {
                    "command": {
                      "name": "SLEEPMONITOR",
                      "commandType": "GET",
                      "commandActive": "OFF",
                      "startTime": "12:30",
                      "endTime": "08:41"
                    },
                    "deviceId": 1,
                    "timestamp": 1575812839756
                  }
                },
                "REFUSEDINCALL": {
                  "value": {
                    "command": {
                      "name": "REFUSEDINCALL",
                      "commandType": "GET",
                      "commandActive": "ON",
                      "acceptTelNo": [
                        "031-111-1111",
                        "031-111-1112",
                        "031-111-1113",
                        "031-111-1114",
                        "031-111-1115"
                      ]
                    },
                    "deviceId": 1,
                    "timestamp": 1575812839756
                  }
                },
                "EMERGENCYNO": {
                  "value": {
                    "command": {
                      "name": "EMERGENCYNO",
                      "commandType": "SET",
                      "commandActive": "OFF",
                      "contacts": [
                        {
                          "sequence": 1,
                          "firstname": "John",
                          "lastname": "Doe",
                          "gender": "M",
                          "email": "john.doe@domain.com",
                          "telno": "+41798252123"
                        },
                        {
                          "sequence": 2,
                          "firstname": "Jane",
                          "lastname": "Doe",
                          "gender": "F",
                          "email": "jane.doe@domain.com",
                          "telno": "+41798252321"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    "deviceId": 1,
                    "timestamp": 1575812839756
                  }
                },
                "TALKMODE": {
                  "value": {
                    "command": {
                      "name": "TALKMODE",
                      "commandType": "GET",
                      "commandActive": "OFF",
                      "answer": "AUTOANSWER"
                    },
                    "deviceId": 1,
                    "timestamp": 1575812839756
                  }
                },
                "HEARTRATE": {
                  "value": {
                    "command": {
                      "name": "HEARTRATE",
                      "commandType": "SET",
                      "commandActive": "OFF"
                    },
                    "deviceId": 1,
                    "timestamp": 1575812839756
                  }
                },
                "HEARTRATEMONITOR": {
                  "value": {
                    "command": {
                      "name": "HEARTRATEMONITOR",
                      "commandType": "GET",
                      "commandActive": "ON",
                      "startTime": "08:00",
                      "endTime": "12:00",
                      "measurementInterval": 2,
                      "transmitInterval": 15
                    },
                    "deviceId": 1,
                    "timestamp": 1575812839756
                  }
                },
                "LOCATION": {
                  "value": {
                    "command": {
                      "name": "LOCATION",
                      "commandType": "GET",
                      "commandActive": "OFF"
                    },
                    "deviceId": 1,
                    "timestamp": 1575812839756
                  }
                },
                "GEOFENCE": {
                  "value": {
                    "command": {
                      "name": "GEOFENCE",
                      "commandType": "GET",
                      "commandActive": "ON",
                      "longitude": 50.260393,
                      "latitude": 71.548594,
                      "radius": 1,
                      "interval": 1
                    },
                    "deviceId": 1,
                    "timestamp": 1575812839756
                  }
                },
                "DESTINATION": {
                  "value": {
                    "command": {
                      "name": "DESTINATION",
                      "commandType": "SET",
                      "commandActive": "ON",
                      "longitude": 50.260393,
                      "latitude": 71.548594,
                      "radius": 1,
                      "interval": 1
                    },
                    "deviceId": 1,
                    "timestamp": 1575812839756
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Command was sent to a device.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SendCommandResponseDto"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "Command is incorrect.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "Authorization information is missing or invalid.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "403": {
            "description": "Access token does not have the required scope",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "404": {
            "description": "A device with the specified ID was not found.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "components": {
    "securitySchemes": {
      "OAuth2": {
        "type": "oauth2",
        "flows": {
          "authorizationCode": {
            "authorizationUrl": "https://auth.aidwatch.net/auth/realms/aidwatch/protocol/openid-connect/auth",
            "tokenUrl": "https://auth.aidwatch.net/auth/realms/aidwatch/protocol/openid-connect/token",
            "scopes": {
              "subscribe_device": "Allows subscribe access to a device",
              "send_command": "Allows send access to a device"
            }
          },
          "password": {
            "tokenUrl": "https://auth.aidwatch.net/auth/realms/aidwatch/protocol/openid-connect/token",
            "scopes": {
              "subscribe_device": "Allows subscribe access to a device",
              "send_command": "Allows send access to a device"
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "schemas": {
      "SubscribedDevice": {
        "title": "DeviceDTO",
        "required": [
          "created",
          "enduserId",
          "id",
          "order",
          "product",
          "variation"
        ],
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64",
            "example": 2840
          },
          "product": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64",
            "example": 1
          },
          "variation": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64"
          },
          "order": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64",
            "example": 123
          },
          "created": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "date-time"
          },
          "protocol": {
            "maxLength": 50,
            "minLength": 0,
            "type": "string"
          },
          "imei": {
            "maxLength": 30,
            "minLength": 0,
            "type": "string"
          },
          "telno": {
            "maxLength": 15,
            "minLength": 0,
            "type": "string"
          },
          "deviceToken": {
            "maxLength": 512,
            "minLength": 0,
            "type": "string"
          },
          "enduserId": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64",
            "example": 2840
          }
        }
      },
      "DeviceInfo": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "An object that contains information about a device that wants to subscribe to the Aidwatch Firebase API.",
        "required": [
          "deviceToken"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "deviceToken": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "expected_device_token"
          }
        }
      },
      "Command": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "name",
          "commandType",
          "commandActive"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "name": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "FALLSENSOR",
            "description": "command name"
          },
          "commandType": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "GET",
            "enum": [
              "GET",
              "SET"
            ]
          },
          "commandActive": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": true,
            "enum": [
              "ON",
              "OFF"
            ]
          }
        },
        "discriminator": {
          "propertyName": "name",
          "mapping": {
            "FALLSENSOR": "#/components/schemas/FallSensor",
            "WATCHREMOVE": "#/components/schemas/WatchRemove",
            "LOWBATTERY": "#/components/schemas/LowBattery",
            "WATCHSWITCHOFF": "#/components/schemas/WatchSwitchOff",
            "MEDICINEALERT": "#/components/schemas/MedicineAlert",
            "PEDOMETER": "#/components/schemas/PedoMeter",
            "SLEEPMONITOR": "#/components/schemas/SleepMonitor",
            "REFUSEDINCALL": "#/components/schemas/RefusedInCall",
            "EMERGENCYNO": "#/components/schemas/EmergencyNo",
            "TALKMODE": "#/components/schemas/TalkMode",
            "HEARTRATE": "#/components/schemas/HeartRate",
            "HEARTRATEMONITOR": "#/components/schemas/HeartRateMonitor",
            "LOCATION": "#/components/schemas/Location",
            "GEOFENCE": "#/components/schemas/Geofence",
            "DESTINATION": "#/components/schemas/Destination"
          }
        }
      },
      "SendCommandDto": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "command",
          "deviceId",
          "timestamp"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "command": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Command"
          },
          "deviceId": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64",
            "example": 1,
            "description": "device identifier."
          },
          "timestamp": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64",
            "example": 1575812839756,
            "description": "Timestamp of the response."
          }
        }
      },
      "SendCommandResponseDto": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "id",
          "deviceId",
          "timestamp",
          "command",
          "syncStatus"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64",
            "example": 1,
            "description": "command identifier."
          },
          "deviceId": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64",
            "example": 1,
            "description": "device identifier."
          },
          "command": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Command"
          },
          "syncStatus": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "SENT_TO_DEVICE",
            "description": "Command sync status."
          },
          "timestamp": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64",
            "example": 1575812839756,
            "description": "Timestamp of the response."
          }
        }
      },
      "FallSensor": {
        "example": "FALLSENSOR",
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Example of request to Aidwatch Firebase API that contains the FALLSENSOR command to send to a device.",
        "required": [
          "threshold",
          "screenDelay"
        ],
        "allOf": [
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Command"
          },
          {
            "properties": {
              "threshold": {
                "type": "number",
                "example": 12,
                "description": "The value that needs to be exceeded before an alarm is generated."
              },
              "screenDelay": {
                "type": "number",
                "example": 13,
                "description": "Seconds the warning screen is displayed where the fall alert can be cancelled."
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "WatchRemove": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Example of request to Aidwatch Firebase API that contains the WATCHREMOVE command to send to a device.",
        "required": [
          "startTime",
          "endTime"
        ],
        "allOf": [
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Command"
          },
          {
            "properties": {
              "startTime": {
                "type": "string",
                "pattern": "^\\d{2}:\\d{2}$"
              },
              "endTime": {
                "type": "string",
                "pattern": "^\\d{2}:\\d{2}$"
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "LowBattery": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Example of request to Aidwatch Firebase API that contains the LOWBATTERY command to send to a device.",
        "required": [
          "minBattery"
        ],
        "allOf": [
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Command"
          },
          {
            "properties": {
              "minBattery": {
                "type": "number",
                "example": 12
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "WatchSwitchOff": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Example of request to Aidwatch Firebase API that contains the WATCHSWITCHOFF command to send to a device.",
        "allOf": [
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Command"
          }
        ]
      },
      "MedicineAlert": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Example of request to Aidwatch Firebase API that contains the MEDICINEALERT command to send to a device.",
        "required": [
          "alarmTimes"
        ],
        "allOf": [
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Command"
          },
          {
            "properties": {
              "alarmTimes": {
                "type": "array",
                "items": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "pattern": "^\\d{2}:\\d{2}$",
                  "example": [
                    "08:00",
                    "12:00",
                    "18:00"
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "PedoMeter": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Example of request to Aidwatch Firebase API that contains the PEDOMETER command to send to a device.",
        "required": [
          "startTime",
          "endTime"
        ],
        "allOf": [
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Command"
          },
          {
            "properties": {
              "startTime": {
                "type": "string",
                "pattern": "^\\d{2}:\\d{2}$"
              },
              "endTime": {
                "type": "string",
                "pattern": "^\\d{2}:\\d{2}$"
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "SleepMonitor": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Example of request to Aidwatch Firebase API that contains the SLEEPMONITOR command to send to a device.",
        "required": [
          "startTime",
          "endTime"
        ],
        "allOf": [
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Command"
          },
          {
            "properties": {
              "startTime": {
                "type": "string",
                "pattern": "^\\d{2}:\\d{2}$"
              },
              "endTime": {
                "type": "string",
                "pattern": "^\\d{2}:\\d{2}$"
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "RefusedInCall": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Example of request to Aidwatch Firebase API that contains the REFUSEDINCALL command to send to a device.",
        "required": [
          "acceptTelNo"
        ],
        "allOf": [
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Command"
          },
          {
            "properties": {
              "acceptTelNo": {
                "type": "array",
                "items": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "example": [
                    "031-111-1111",
                    "031-111-1112",
                    "031-111-1113",
                    "031-111-1114",
                    "031-111-1115"
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "EmergencyNo": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Example of request to Aidwatch Firebase API that contains the EMERGENCYNO command to send to a device.",
        "required": [
          "contacts"
        ],
        "allOf": [
          {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Command"
          },
          {
            "properties": {
              "contacts": {
                "type": "array",
                "items": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Contact"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "Contact": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Emergency contact",
        "required": [
          "telNo"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "sequence": {
            "type": "integer",
            "example": 1
          },
          "firstname": {
            "maxLength": 50,
            "minLength": 0,
            "type": "string",
            "example": "Jack"
          },
          "lastname": {
            "maxLength": 100,
            "minLength": 0,
            "type": "string",
            "example": "Loonen"
          },
          "gender": {
            "maxLength": 1,
            "minLength": 1,
            "type": "string",
            "example": "M"
          },
          "telno": {
            "maxLength": 50,
